Package: rcforge
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, 
         bash (>= 4.0), 
         findutils, 
         sed, 
         grep, 
         coreutils
Recommends: zsh
Description: Universal shell configuration system for Bash and Zsh
 rcForge is a flexible, modular shell configuration framework that:
 .
 * Provides a unified approach to managing shell environments
 * Works across multiple machines and shell types
 * Supports both Bash and Zsh
 * Offers machine-specific and global configurations
 * Includes a powerful include system for modular functions
